Package br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.utils

package br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.utils
This package contains utility classes for the domain layer of the OmniCommunicator.

The utility classes in this package provide common functionality that is used across the domain layer, such as printing the application banner. These utilities help to reduce code duplication and increase code reuse.
